ISLAMABAD, Feb 10 (APP):Prime Minister Imran Khan on Wednesday welcomed the assurance given by his Sri Lankan counterpart Mahinda Rajapaksa in the Parliament, allowing Muslims to bury those died from the Covid-19 pandemic.
“We welcome Sri Lankan PM Mahinda Rajapaksa’s assurance given in Sri Lankan Parliament today allowing Muslims to bury those who died from COVID19,” Imran Khan said in a tweet posted on his twitter handle.
